WEBVTT

00:00:30.333 --> 00:00:33.208
Their faces were full of tears.

00:00:34.042 --> 00:00:37.875
I had the opportunity to go in
and be with them.

00:00:39.250 --> 00:00:41.309
And they were all around me.

00:00:41.333 --> 00:00:45.268
They were little ones,

00:00:45.292 --> 00:00:48.750
some of them not older
than five years old.

00:00:49.875 --> 00:00:52.476
And they were saying to me,

00:00:52.500 --> 00:00:54.518
(Spanish) "Sácame de aquí."

00:00:54.542 --> 00:00:55.917
"Get me out of here."

00:00:57.708 --> 00:00:59.309
(Spanish) "Por favor, ayúdame."

00:00:59.333 --> 00:01:00.625
"Please, help me."